mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From The Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On The Record and Record Report", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "16th National Convention", "Lift and Use", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Spotlight On A Caller's Association", "More Expo '67 Square Dancing in New Brunswick", "Down Under Square Dance Institute in New Zealand", "Some Summer Square Dancing", "Interview: Bob Page", "Style Series: Comfortable Equivalents", "Round The World of Square Dancing", "SIO Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Jerry Haag", "Paging The Roundancers: Ray and Eloise Appel", and "Experimental Lab: Grand Spin".
